    "Name": "Indra",
    "Details": "The Indra Infantry Transport excels at its role as a personnel carrier with three tons of cargo space. It can deliver its payload swiftly to the battlefield with a top speed of 86 km/h, though not as fast as some other transports can. It compensates for that with five tons of Ferro-Fibrous armor that keep its crew safe from even the most damaging gun in the Clan arsenal. The Indra's main weapon is an ER PPC, capable of threatening armored vehicles and mechs alike. Four Machine Guns in a turret mount serve to support its own infantry forces in battle against enemy infantry.\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Wheeled: Fast in open ground, slow in rough terrain.</color></b>\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Fusion: Expensive engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 5/8 Hex: 150/240 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous (C)\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       152     20\n<b>Left</b>         100     20\n<b>Right</b>       100     20\n<b>Rear</b>         70     20\n<b>Turret</b>      105     20\n\n<b>Total</b>      527    100\n",
